              ],
              "free_text": [
                "The reaction products were detected with DINEX",
                "array. Four delta-E-E telescopes were located around",
                "the target in a cylindrical configuration. The",
                "thickness of the E layers was 40 mum, while the E-res",
                "stages were 1000 mum thick. Each detector had an active",
                "area of 48.5 mm*48.5 mm and both the p-side and the",
                "n-side were segmented into 16 strips, allowing a pixel",
